      "content": "DONE (commit 9f6f270):\n\n**Change 1 — source_msg_id:**\n- `src/db.ts`: `Task` interface gets `source_msg_id: number | null`; `startTask()` gains optional `sourceMsgId` param; INSERT includes `source_msg_id`; migration adds `ALTER TABLE tasks ADD COLUMN source_msg_id INTEGER`\n- `src/mcp-server.ts`: `delegate_task` schema gets `source_msg_id` optional integer param with description; handler destructures it and passes to both `startTask()` call paths\n\n**Change 2 — DB table rename:**\n- `src/db.ts`: `CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS tasks` (fresh installs); migration `ALTER TABLE activities RENAME TO tasks`; all SQL strings updated (`INSERT INTO tasks`, `UPDATE tasks`, `SELECT * FROM tasks`, `SELECT id FROM tasks`); index CREATE statements updated to reference `tasks` table\n\n`npm run build` clean.",
